</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Bringing Austria, Finland, Sweden and Norway into the European Union will
mean the EU budget needs to be expanded by more than Dollars 1bn next year,
the European Parliament said yesterday. The parliament proposed the draft EU
budget for 1995 be increased by Ecu800m (Pounds 629m) to reflect the
