(USDollars 14.2m), or about 45 cents per Dominion share.
GMA decided not to press ahead with its ADollars 182m bid for Dominion last
July, after the target company granted NBHP an option to take an 80 per cent
interest in Dominion's ADollars 500m Yakabindie nickel project in Western
Australia.
